msgid "Generate counts per contact circle when calculating network count"
msgstr "Generér tal per kontaktkreds når netværkstal udregnes"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:582
msgid ""
"On systems with users that heavily use contact circles the query can be very"
" expensive."
msgstr "På instanser med brugere, der har mange kontaktkredse, kan forespørgslen være meget krævende."

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:583
msgid "Process \"view\" activities"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:583
msgid ""
"\"view\" activities are mostly geberated by Peertube systems. Per default "
"they are not processed for performance reasons. Only activate this option on"
" performant system."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:584
msgid "Days, after which a contact is archived"
msgstr "Dage indtil en kontakt arkiveres."

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:584
msgid ""
"Number of days that we try to deliver content or to update the contact data "
"before we archive a contact."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:586
msgid "Maximum number of parallel workers"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:586
#, php-format
msgid ""
"On shared hosters set this to %d. On larger systems, values of %d are great."
" Default value is %d."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:587
msgid "Maximum load for workers"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:587
msgid "Maximum load that causes a cooldown before each worker function call."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:588
msgid "Enable fastlane"
msgstr "Slå \"fastlane\" til"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:588
msgid ""
"When enabed, the fastlane mechanism starts an additional worker if processes"
" with higher priority are blocked by processes of lower priority."
msgstr "Når dette aktiveres vil \"fastlane\"-mekanismen starte en yderligere \"worker\" hvis processer med høj prioriteret blokeres af processer med lav prioritet."

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:589
msgid "Decoupled receiver"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:589
msgid ""
"Decouple incoming ActivityPub posts by processing them in the background via"
" a worker process. Only enable this on fast systems."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:590
msgid "Fetch replies mode"
msgstr "Metode for at hente kommentarer"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:590
msgid "Missing replies can be fetched upon receipt of an ActivityPub post."
msgstr "Manglende svar kan blive hentet ved modtagelsen af et ActivityPub-opslag."

